1.2 Respondent Characteristics

1.2.1 Inclusion Group Representation
Table 1.1 shows the representation of inclusion groups among client survey respondents.


Code
dplt_client_ig &lt;- d_long_raw |&gt; 
    group_by(inclusion_group_label) |&gt;
    summarize(
        N = n(),
        n = sum(ig_member),
        p = n / N
    ) |&gt;
    mutate(
        pn = glue::glue("{scales::percent(p, accuracy = 1)} ({n}/{N})")
    ) |&gt;
    arrange(desc(p)) 

dplt_client_ig |&gt;
    select(inclusion_group_label, sample_representation = pn) |&gt;
    arrange(inclusion_group_label) |&gt; 
    gt() |&gt;
    gtExtras::gt_theme_538() |&gt;
    tab_source_note(
        source_note = dl_button(dplt_client_ig, "xp-client-igo")
    )






